Install:
--------
1) RPM users:
	simply install the package:  
	rpm -Uhv nxshell-....rpm

2) Manual installation:
	unpack the tar ball: tar -xvzf nxshell.tar.bz2
	cd nxshell
	make
	sudo make install

Test:

	nxshell -l user@host

Help:
-----
try nxshell --help for more information


Have fun :-)
Marcus
